2. Key Technical Concepts:
   - curl/libcurl source code (version curl-8_12_0)
   - OpenSSL TLS certificate verification via Subject Alternative Names (SAN)
   - Null-byte injection attacks in TLS certificates
   - SSL password callback buffer overflow
   - Cookie domain matching per RFC 6265 (tailmatch/subdomain boundary checking)
   - HTTP cookie `__Secure-` and `__Host-` prefix matching (case-sensitivity requirements)
